headline.print_headline: Part of Fla. History to Step Back Into Spotlight
headline.main: Part of Fla. History to Step Back Into Spotlight

lead_paragraph: Hidden behind live oaks and magnolias near the Florida Governor's Mansion, a historic house that symbolizes much of the state's terrible past and transformation will soon have its doors opened to the public.
